data.description: Discover this special location. First time on the market, this property spans almost an acre within the city limits of Scotts Valley at the end of a private and quiet street with beautiful views. Offering a rare combo of country-like tranquility yet walking convenience to Cinelux, Skypark, shopping/dining & community gatherings. Adjacent to180 acres of open space, offering picturesque vistas from every angle. While the potential for future updates such as remodeling the kit & baths present an exciting opportunity to customize, this location is a once & a rare opportunity. Stunning great room is the heart of the home w/gleaming hardwood flrs, airy ambiance & walls of dual pane windows framing the breathtaking views. Expansive wrap-around decking provides an outdoor space for al fresco dining or simply relishing the views. This home enters & lives like a single lvl yet boasts a bonus family room & convenient 1/2 bath downstairs. Multiple glass doors beckon you to the sun-drenched property, where ample space awaits.
